quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,25,"Wama arsalna min qablika minrasoolin illa noohee ilayhi annahu la ilahailla ana faAAbudoon"
  21,26,"Waqaloo ittakhatha arrahmanuwaladan subhanahu bal AAibadun mukramoon"
  21,27,"La yasbiqoonahu bilqawliwahum bi-amrihi yaAAmaloon"
  21,28,"YaAAlamu ma bayna aydeehim wamakhalfahum wala yashfaAAoona illa limani irtadawahum min khashyatihi mushfiqoon"
  21,29,"Waman yaqul minhum innee ilahun mindoonihi fathalika najzeehi jahannama kathalikanajzee aththalimeen"
  21,30,"Awa lam yara allatheenakafaroo anna assamawati wal-ardakanata ratqan fafataqnahuma wajaAAalnamina alma-i kulla shay-in hayyin afalayu/minoon"
  21,31,"WajaAAalna fee al-ardi rawasiyaan tameeda bihim wajaAAalna feeha fijajansubulan laAAallahum yahtadoon"
  21,32,"WajaAAalna assamaasaqfan mahfoothan wahum AAan ayatihamuAAridoon"
  21,33,"Wahuwa allathee khalaqa allayla wannaharawashshamsa walqamara kullun fee falakin yasbahoon"
  21,34,"Wama jaAAalna libasharin minqablika alkhulda afa-in mitta fahumu alkhalidoon"
  21,35,"Kullu nafsin tha-iqatu almawtiwanablookum bishsharri walkhayri fitnatanwa-ilayna turjaAAoon"
